   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.06" end="00:00:04.30" region="speaker">This modification allows you to change the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.30" end="00:00:06.06" region="speaker">geographic scope of coverage for your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:06.06" end="00:00:07.56" region="speaker">contract.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.56" end="00:00:10.23" region="speaker">Select the desired SIN from the dropdown menu</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.23" end="00:00:13.33" region="speaker">then click &quot;Update SIN Details.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:13.33" end="00:00:15.43" region="speaker">The SIN details will show you the current scope</p>
         <p begin="00:00:15.43" end="00:00:18.26" region="speaker">associated with your chosen SIN.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.26" end="00:00:20.53" region="speaker">From the dropdown menu, select what your new</p>
         <p begin="00:00:20.53" end="00:00:22.76" region="speaker">geographic coverage Will be.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.76" end="00:00:25.30" region="speaker">When you are satisfied with your selection click</p>
         <p begin="00:00:25.30" end="00:00:27.20" region="speaker">&quot;Update This SIN.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:27.20" end="00:00:29.76" region="speaker">If you would like to make changes to your scope or</p>
         <p begin="00:00:29.76" end="00:00:31.83" region="speaker">if you have made an error and wish to delete the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:31.83" end="00:00:34.73" region="speaker">change in scope you may do so with the &quot;Edit&quot; and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:34.73" end="00:00:36.56" region="speaker">&quot;Delete&quot; links.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:36.56" end="00:00:39.10" region="speaker">Otherwise, provide a description about what has</p>
         <p begin="00:00:39.10" end="00:00:42.13" region="speaker">necessitated your change in Geographic coverage as</p>
         <p begin="00:00:42.13" end="00:00:44.16" region="speaker">well as any other pertinent details in the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:44.16" end="00:00:46.03" region="speaker">textbox below.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:46.03" end="00:00:48.56" region="speaker">When you are finished click &quot;Save and Continue.&quot;</p>
    </div>
